{"tid":1094391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客殺入貝澳露營　本地營友嘆：逼過劏房","createTime":"2019-04-06T09:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T04:45:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ba02f72b3b860938e7441380a18c7931924b3907","tid":1094391,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190406163211\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190406163211&h=a45a9ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清明節一連3天假期，最適合遠足郊遊，然而位於大嶼山的貝澳營地營位昨日及今日(5、6日)迅速爆滿，有營友苦嘆貝澳營疑被內地團「攻佔」，港人清明放假想覓一處寧靜地方露營放鬆都難。東網今致電貝澳營辦事處查詢，職員指營地54個營位全部爆滿，明日(7日)營位會繼續以先到先得方式即場申請。 <br />\n<br />\n有營友&lrm;昨上載照片至Facebook群組「PLAY HARD玩硬」，苦訴貝澳慘被內地團佔領。照片所見，露營人士插針式在營內紮帳篷，帳篷間僅有數厘米距離，擠迫情況直逼劏房。營友認為內地人士插針式進駐營地，根本無法享受郊野的寧靜，「也不知露營樂趣何在」。 <br />\n<br />\n貝澳營地是康樂文化事務署轄下的營地，位置鄰近貝澳泳灘，內設燒烤爐、洗手間及更衣室等設施，風景優美又遠離市區，不少市民都選擇假日到該營感受大自然氣氛。康文署網頁表示，申請人只須年滿18歲並持有香港身份證或有效旅遊證件，即可以先到先得方式即場申請貝澳營地的營位。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190406163211\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190406163211&h=fc4437ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190406163211\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190406163211&h=7d6152ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/bkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190406%2Fbkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001.html&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=a902cd2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/bkn-20190406160425779-0406_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dfc6d9a605e82ac649f7152c16208422949a2452","tid":1094391,"uid":84585,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa6d1ffac400690241594063b109b31b30ecf82a","tid":1094391,"uid":27451,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"點解d蝗咁鍾意黎香港?"},{"pid":"48d6654762d656c311b60984e0ddefb438c5a1f0","tid":1094391,"uid":40470,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"熱烈支持中國法輪功在此露營"},{"pid":"46605ae4b6e8319e39a298f12b78e247720ec50e","tid":1094391,"uid":171192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e665ff8a3ee2645f61c1604242ecc6feedc4ed","tid":1094391,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"班本地營友有無10%人支持本土派<br />\n支持攬炒"},{"pid":"5077173c0283f80ad163687472e7749fc4964429","tid":1094391,"uid":35430,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲所到之處一片狼藉"},{"pid":"095360ffef5e93224132e55547094e7b9255e9cc","tid":1094391,"uid":126648,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"成個集中營咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dddca3bc9de9b2c69437aede535bd30f6d4a74","tid":1094391,"uid":50310,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"屌你啦！去個廁所就知道要等幾耐"},{"pid":"978c6048ce878d229191606791d32ab5f9d6b525","tid":1094391,"uid":145277,"like":34,"